properties.otherAdvice:
Two Mile section of Jenolan Caves Rd is now open.

properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - Saturday 14 to Monday 16 March - SURRY HILLS Chalmers Street between Cleveland Street, Chippendale AND Devonshire Street
properties.otherAdvice:

Clearways are strict no parking zones even for local residents and RMS Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs carefully as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.
